<br>
That being said, I'm a lvl 50 shade, and I don't give a rats ass about buff bots. I don't use em, and don't care if anyone else does. Why? Cause I don't solo. I'm much more usefull to my realm if I'm attacking or defending keeps (especially when the enemy is there, weeee).<br>
<br>
People really need to think about the larger picture than just their own little world, making any changes to the conc system will have widespread ramifications that I just know the same people who loby for its cause will scream nerf the loudest if it ever got implemented. However, I seriously doubt you'll see anything change here.<br>
<br>
And would you rather Mythic spend thier time trying to find out how to eliminate buff bots, or actually finish some of their bigger projects that will help everyone, not just your solo'ing self? hm? <p><img src=http://www.pakcafan.com/daoc/images/cougsig.jpg></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub175.ezboard.com/uubergnome563.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ubergnome563</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/7/02 4:22:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3701.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> You are kinda missing the &quot;larger picture&quot;<br>
<br>
who said anything about soloing?  I dont leave the PK w/o a group.<br>
<br>
As a matter of fact, I had a group with me at the time, all of which who were buffed (same bot, i wasnt as buffed as the bot's owner either).  <br>
<br>
Adding a reasonable range to buffs, such as from the alb PK to alb Milefort in emain, would allow for scouting, and make buffing classes participate in rvr to be effective (which is the point of the post - not nerf buff bots), w/o having any real major &quot;ramifications&quot;<br>
<br>
The point is:<br>
<br>
BUFF SPECS CAN OPERATE AT FULL SPECLINE EFFECIENCY W/O ACTUALLY PARTICIPATING IN RVR BATTLES UNLIKE EVERY OTHER CLASS IN THE GAME WHICH HAS TO DIRECTLY PARTICIPATE IN BATTLES TO BE USEFUL.<br>
<br>
Find me ONE, non buff spec'd class, who's specline does not involve some form of RVR combat.<br>
<br>
Healer type?  Have to be in battle to heal those taking damage, cant do that in the PK all day<br>
<br>
Nuker?  Have to be in battle to nuke<br>
<br>
ARcher?  see nuker<br>
<br>
Melee?  Have to be in melee range..<br>
<br>
Assassin?   See melee<br>
<br>
Any others?<br>
<br>
O wait!  buffer!   can buff inside the PK, and remain there  due to the unlimited range / time on conc buffs.  <br>
<br>
Nobody's talking about isolated buff botted infiltrators soloing rvr, look at the real big picture.  And if i had those buffs in a keep raid, I could easily drop 15 defenders myself before the other 12 people with me bashed down level 4 doors<br>
<br>
